{"tid":719403,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"［親生仔］Pixel 3高清設計圖已被發佈 爆料大神：這就是Google Pixel 3","createTime":"2018-06-27T11:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T13:48:03.000Z","uid":1714,"like":3,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"ff653a8d5f2234d5f490be4351241b72422dc3be","tid":719403,"uid":1714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:40:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-PC2q3Lz1WFg/WzNzhDDYG8I/AAAAAAABmWw/TZyloulLAbYeO4Z8rJ1qVngYIKooS3p5gCLcBGAs/s1600/pixel3inhd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F3.bp.blogspot.com%2F-PC2q3Lz1WFg%2FWzNzhDDYG8I%2FAAAAAAABmWw%2FTZyloulLAbYeO4Z8rJ1qVngYIKooS3p5gCLcBGAs%2Fs1600%2Fpixel3inhd.png&h=3641e4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.thealpha.app/2018/06/pixel3inhd.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thealpha.app%2F2018%2F06%2Fpixel3inhd.html&d=KEBMhe5rGA8bf52ZRo792TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=2a0d223d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thealpha.app/2018/06/pixel3inhd.html</a></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Google Pixel 3系列將會喺幾個月後發佈，而一直都未有啲來源可信嘅爆料，之前關於Pixel 3嘅消息一直都受疑。而今日，知名爆料大神@OnLeaks卒之發佈咗Google Pixel 3同Pixel 3 XL嘅3D高清設計圖。 <br />\n<br />\n喺設計圖入面，可以確定到Google Pixel 3會承傳Pixel 2 XL嘅設計，盡量縮少上下巴，用盡正面空間嚟做到5.4吋屏幕。而Pixel 3 XL就會用好似iPhone X咁用M字額屏幕設計，大小為6.2吋。無論係大機定細機，Pixel 3均配備單鏡主鏡頭，而同Pixel 2唔同嘅就係SIM卡槽會放喺電話嘅下方，而唔係左側。目前可以確定的就係Pixel 3會行Snapdragon 845流動平台，第二粒自拍鏡頭嘅存在亦受疑，可以只係感應器而唔係鏡頭。</span>"},{"pid":"6baf665f3aff1bb99f2f2192f5a30851889e7faa","tid":719403,"uid":92477,"like":4,"dislike":26,"score":-22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T11:42:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/27/194201_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F27%2F194201_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=04d9209e&s={SIZE}\" />